Tech Stack

Frontend: React (Hooks, functional components)

Styling: Tailwind CSS (utility-first) + custom CSS tokens

Icons: lucide-react

3D: @react-three/fiber, @react-three/drei

Bundler/Dev: Vite (recommended)

